advisories.title: Deserialization of Untrusted Data in codeception/codeception
advisories.description: This affects the package codeception/codeception from 4.0.0 before 4.1.22 and before 3.1.3. The RunProcess class can be leveraged as a gadget to run arbitrary commands on a system that is deserializing user input without validation.
